name: Hajime Kinoko x Ashinaga Tokyo Orphans Charity Airdrop
description: Commemorative special edition of Samsara, the groundbreaking world's first Shibari Rope Art AR NFT by Hajime Kinoko. 20% Royalty on all transactions will go to Ashinaga, the Tokyo orphans charity which we at RPM hope will be used to support the arts in orphans. Photo taken by Hajime Kinoko.
